#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:1
msgid "Live Trading S1.3 设计理念与架构"
msgstr "Live Trading S1.3 Design Philosophy and Architecture"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:3
msgid ""
"本文从设计视角解释 S1.3 的 live trading 改造思路：为什么这样分层、如何"
"保持兼容、以及这些设计如何帮助后续扩展。"
msgstr ""
"This article explains, from a design perspective, the live trading "
"refactor approach for S1.3: why the layering is done this way, how "
"compatibility is maintained, and how these designs help with future "
"extensions."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:5
msgid "0. 文档定位"
msgstr "0. Document Positioning"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:7
msgid "本文是设计说明，不是使用教程"
msgstr "This document is a design specification, not a user tutorial."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:8
msgid "重点回答“为什么这样做”，而不是“如何一步步操作”"
msgstr ""
"It focuses on answering “why we do it this way”, rather than “how to "
"operate step by step”"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:9
msgid ""
"若需要实操路径，请转到 `live_trading/2-configuration-and-run.md` 与 "
"`tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-broker-walkthrough.md`"
msgstr ""
"If you need a hands-on path, please go to `live_trading/2-"
"configuration-and-run.md` and `tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-broker-"
"walkthrough.md`"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:11
msgid "1. 设计目标"
msgstr "1. Design Goals"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:13
msgid "在不破坏既有用户路径的前提下，提升 live 链路的可校验性与可审计性"
msgstr ""
"Without breaking existing user flows, improve the verifiability and "
"auditability of the live path"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:14
msgid "把风险控制前置到“下单写库之前”"
msgstr ""
"Move risk control forward to “before placing orders and writing to the "
"database”"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:15
msgid "抽象 Broker 适配层，为未来真实柜台接入预留稳定边界"
msgstr ""
"Abstract the Broker adapter layer to reserve a stable boundary for "
"future integration with real broker front ends"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:17
msgid "2. 分层结构"
msgstr "2. Layered Structure"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:19
msgid "S1.3 的 live 相关职责可抽象为："
msgstr "The live-related responsibilities of S1.3 can be abstracted as:"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:21
msgid "`Operator`：策略运行调度与信号来源"
msgstr "`Operator`: strategy execution scheduling and signal source"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:22
msgid "`Trader`：订单意图落地、风险闸门与执行协调"
msgstr ""
"`Trader`: materialize order intent, risk gating, and execution "
"coordination"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:23
msgid "`RiskManager`：纯逻辑规则评估，不依赖 IO"
msgstr "`RiskManager`: pure logical rule evaluation, no IO dependencies"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:24
msgid "`Broker`：提交、取消、回报、连接语义"
msgstr "`Broker`: submit, cancel, report, and connection semantics"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:25
msgid "`trade_io`：订单/成交数据契约校验"
msgstr "`trade_io`: contract validation for order/trade data"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:27
msgid "3. 关键设计原则"
msgstr "3. Key design principles"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:29
msgid "3.1 契约先行"
msgstr "3.1 Contract-first"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:31
msgid ""
"订单 dict 与成交 dict 在边界处校验，避免“结构错了还能跑”导致的静默错"
"误。"
msgstr ""
"Validate the order dict and fill dict at the boundary to avoid silent "
"errors caused by “it still runs even when the structure is wrong”."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:33
msgid "3.2 风控前置"
msgstr "3.2 Shift risk controls left"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:35
msgid "风险评估在写库和入队之前完成，拒单不污染执行数据。"
msgstr ""
"Risk assessment is completed before writing to the database and "
"enqueueing, so rejected orders do not contaminate execution data."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:37
msgid "3.3 适配解耦"
msgstr "3.3 Adapter decoupling"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:39
msgid ""
"通过 broker adapter API 承载未来接入，降低 Trader 与具体柜台的耦合度。"
msgstr ""
"Carry future integrations via the broker adapter API to reduce "
"coupling between Trader and specific broker systems."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:41
msgid "3.4 可审计"
msgstr "3.4 Auditable"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:43
msgid "拒因以 `rule_id` 和英文 `reason` 对外可见，支持运维检索与复盘。"
msgstr ""
"Rejection reasons are externally visible via `rule_id` and an English "
"`reason`, supporting ops search and post-incident review."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:45
msgid "4. 典型疑难点与取舍"
msgstr "4. Typical tricky points and trade-offs"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:47
msgid "4.1 拒单兼容语义"
msgstr "4.1 Rejection-order compatibility semantics"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:49
msgid ""
"保持历史兼容（拒单可表现为空结果），同时增强可见性（CLI/TUI 摘要 + 日"
"志）。"
msgstr ""
"Maintain backward compatibility (rejections can appear as empty "
"results) while improving visibility (CLI/TUI summary + logs)."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:51
msgid "4.2 新旧链路并存"
msgstr "4.2 Coexistence of new and legacy flows"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:53
msgid "保留 legacy queue 兼容路径，避免一次性迁移带来的回归风险。"
msgstr ""
"Keep the legacy queue compatibility path to avoid regression risk from "
"a one-shot migration."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:55
msgid "4.3 状态一致性"
msgstr "4.3 State consistency"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:57
msgid ""
"分批成交场景下，状态应以累计成交量为准，减少用户观察到的语义偏差。"
msgstr ""
"In partial-fill scenarios, status should be based on the cumulative "
"filled volume to reduce semantic discrepancies observed by users."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:59
msgid "5. 与 S2.1 的关系"
msgstr "5. Relationship with S2.1"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:61
msgid "S1.3 不是柜台接入终点，而是前置地基："
msgstr ""
"S1.3 is not the end point of broker integration, but the foundational "
"groundwork:"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:63
msgid "先稳定接口边界"
msgstr "Stabilize the interface boundaries first"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:64
msgid "再逐步接入真实柜台"
msgstr "Then gradually connect to real broker systems."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:65
msgid "最后在不破坏上层用法的前提下扩展能力"
msgstr "Finally, extend capabilities without breaking upstream usage."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:67
msgid "6. 对用户行为的影响"
msgstr "6. Impact on user behavior"

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:69
msgid "配置错误更早暴露"
msgstr "Configuration errors are exposed earlier."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:70
msgid "拒单原因更容易定位"
msgstr "Rejection reasons are easier to pinpoint."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:71
msgid "live 运行中的状态变化更容易解释"
msgstr "State changes during live operation are easier to explain."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:72
msgid "扩展第三方 broker 的成本更可控"
msgstr "The cost of extending third-party brokers is more controllable."

#: ../../source/design/10-live-trading-s1.3-architecture.md:74
msgid "7. 相关阅读"
msgstr "7. Further reading"

